ntrol sliders.</li><li>2022-03-04: adds the Cyrillic/Ukrainian, Hebrew and =
Arabic alphabets as options.</li><li>2021-09-03: vibration (on phones) does=
 not stop prematurely [thanks Richard].</li><li>2021-09-02: vibration (on p=
hones) now better synchronised with the sound.</li></ul><button id=3D"morse=
Changelog" class=3D"small see-more action">See more</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
